# Python Microservice Workout

### how to run docker

`
docker-compose up
`

### if there is an issue with compose up or connection

```
docker-compose down
docker system prune --force --volumes
docker-compose up -d
```

https://stackoverflow.com/questions/48194404/docker-compose-up-on-windows-failed-with-error-on-mysql-container-step


### how to build
```
docker-compose build
```

### how to generate migrations
```
docker-compose run web alembic revision --autogenerate -m "${migrationMessage}"
```
